data.description: RARE FIND in Fort Mill! Full brick home on 1.6 acres! No HOA dues! Plenty of privacy with the woods in the back! Huge front porch perfect for enjoying your morning coffee! Relax on the expansive back deck while you enjoy your friends and loved ones splashing in the saltwater pool. No shortage of parking with an attached two car garage, plus a detached two car garage/storage building that's heated and cooled. Lots of driveway areas to park additional cars, RV's etc. Kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, white cabinets and the chef in the house will appreciate the gas cook stove. Cathedral ceiling in family room and kitchen makes the home feel extra spacious. Updated primary bath with dual sinks, oversized tile surround shower and walk in closet, plus both full bathrooms feature heated flooring. Home has tankless water heater and tons of storage. Fort Mill Schools!
